# Projects & invoicing

## Primary store: Supabase (UI)

- Web app in `app/` — see `supabase/README.md`.
- Tables: `clients`, `projects`, `time_entries`, `invoices`, `payments`, `organization_settings`.
- Unbilled time: `time_entries.invoice_id IS NULL`.
- Company block and tax flags: `organization_settings` (or `company/profile.local.md` for agents).

## Rules

- One row per time entry; never delete billed entries without owner approval.
- `rate_override` on a row overrides project `default_hourly_rate` for that entry only.
- Invoice PDF uses settings from Supabase `organization_settings`.
- Mark invoice status (draft → sent → paid) and record payments in the app.
